<CONSTANT C-TABLELEN 180>

<GLOBAL C-TABLE <ITABLE NONE 180>>

<GLOBAL C-DEMONS 180>

<GLOBAL C-INTS 180>

<CONSTANT C-INTLEN 6>

<CONSTANT C-ENABLED? 0>

